^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Thank you very much Phillip for your kind words. Welcome everyone to the first of my 8 week course on defense. This course will be in 2 parts. The first 4 weeks will be mostly lecture and examples and the last 4 weeks will be practice hands. This week's topic is opening leads. The topics for the 3 weeks after that are:
